{"data":[{"name":"113:1","price":"[ای پیامبر،] بگو: «به پروردگار سپیده‌دم پناه می‌برم،","arabic":"قُلۡ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ ٱلۡفَلَقِ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6226,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"qul aʿūdhu birabbi al-falaqi ","translations":["Say","I seek refuge","in (the) Lord","(of) the dawn","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","aʿūdhu","birabbi","al-falaqi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,360],[2,360,1280],[3,1280,2110],[4,2110,3005]]}},{"name":"113:2","price":"از شرِ تمام آنچه آفریده است،","arabic":"مِن شَرِّ مَا خَلَقَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6227,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"min sharri mā khalaqa ","translations":["From","(the) evil","(of) what","He created","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["min","sharri","mā","khalaqa",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,940],[2,940,2040],[3,2040,2380],[4,2380,3595]]}},{"name":"113:3","price":"و از شر تاریکی شب، آنگاه که همه جا را فراگیرد،","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ غَاسِقٍ إِذَا وَقَبَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6228,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri ghāsiqin idhā waqaba ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) darkness","when","it spreads","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","ghāsiqin","idhā","waqaba",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,740],[2,740,2140],[3,2140,3250],[4,3250,3870],[5,3870,4945]]}},{"name":"113:4","price":"و از شر [زنان جادوگر] که با افسون در گره‌ها می‌دمند.","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ ٱلنَّفَّٰثَٰتِ فِي ٱلۡعُقَدِ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6229,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri al-nafāthāti fī al-ʿuqadi ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) the blowers","in","the knots","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","al-nafāthāti","fī","al-ʿuqadi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0